#. translators: %1$s: Settings -> Geolocation link, %2$s:
#. faz_trust_cf_ipcountry_header docs link.
#: admin/views/banner.php:765
#, php-format
msgid ""
"No country signal is available on this install. Multi-banner geo-routing "
"will resolve every visitor to \"unknown\" and fall back to your match-all / "
"default banner. Configure %1$s with a MaxMind GeoLite2 key, or enable the "
"%2$s if your site sits behind Cloudflare. Without one of these, the targets "
"you set below have no effect."
msgstr ""
"Er is geen landsignaal beschikbaar op deze installatie. Multi-banner geo-"
"routing zal elke bezoeker oplossen als „onbekend“ en terugvallen op uw "
"catch-all/standaard banner. Configureer %1$s met een MaxMind "
"GeoLite2-sleutel, of schakel %2$s in als uw site achter Cloudflare staat. "
"Zonder een van deze opties hebben de onderstaande doelen geen effect."

#: admin/views/banner.php:766
msgid "Settings &raquo; Geolocation"
msgstr "Instellingen &raquo; Geolocatie"

#: admin/views/banner.php:787
msgid "How multi-banner works — quick guide"
msgstr "Hoe multi-banner werkt — snelle handleiding"

#. translators: %1$s: Geo Targeting (tab name), %2$s: Content (tab name).
#: admin/views/banner.php:794
#, php-format
msgid ""
"%1$s (this tab) = <em>WHICH visitors</em> see this banner. Pick countries / "
"regions; the multi-banner picker matches against the visitor's detected "
"country. Leave empty to make this banner the universal fallback."
msgstr ""
"%1$s (dit tabblad) = <em>WELKE bezoekers</em> deze banner zien. Kies "
"landen/regio’s; de multi-banner selector vergelijkt het gedetecteerde land "
"van de bezoeker. Laat leeg om deze banner als universele terugvaloptie in te"
" stellen."

#. translators: %1$s: Content (tab name).
#: admin/views/banner.php:805
#, php-format
msgid ""
"%1$s = <em>WHAT the banner says</em> — title, description, button labels, "
"per-language translations. This is where you put law-specific copy: \"Não "
"vender minhas informações pessoais\" for LGPD (Brazil), \"Do not sell or "
"share my personal information\" for CCPA/CPRA (California 2024+), German "
"consent text for GDPR-DE, and so on. Same banner row, multiple languages."
msgstr ""
"%1$s = <em>WAT DE BANNER ZEGT</em> — titel, beschrijving, knoplabels, "
"vertalingen per taal. Hier plaatst u wetsspecifieke tekst: \"Não vender "
"minhas informações pessoais\" voor LGPD (Brazilië), \"Do not sell or share "
"my personal information\" voor CCPA/CPRA (Californië 2024+), Duitse "
"toestemmingstekst voor AVG-DE, enzovoort. Dezelfde bannerrij, meerdere "
"talen."

#: admin/views/banner.php:813
msgid ""
"<strong>EU</strong> preset = 27 EU + 3 EEA (Iceland, Liechtenstein, Norway)."
" It does <em>not</em> include the UK — pick the <strong>United "
"Kingdom</strong> preset separately when you want a UK-GDPR variant with "
"different copy. To cover EU+UK with one banner, tick both presets."
msgstr ""
"<strong>EU-voorinstelling</strong> = 27 EU + 3 EER (IJsland, Liechtenstein, "
"Noorwegen). Het Verenigd Koninkrijk is <em>niet</em> inbegrepen — kies de "
"<strong>United Kingdom</strong>-voorinstelling afzonderlijk als u een UK-"
"AVG-variant met andere tekst wilt. Om EU+VK met één banner te dekken, vinkt "
"u beide voorinstellingen aan."

