#: admin/views/settings.php:14
msgid "Banner Control"
msgstr "Bannerbeheer"

#: admin/views/settings.php:23
msgid ""
"When disabled, the cookie consent banner will not appear on your site and no"
" scripts will be blocked."
msgstr ""
"Indien uitgeschakeld, verschijnt de cookie-toestemmingsbanner niet op je "
"site en zullen er geen scripts geblokkeerd worden."

#: admin/views/settings.php:26
msgid "Excluded Pages"
msgstr "Uitgesloten pagina’s"

#: admin/views/settings.php:27
msgid "One per line: page ID or URL pattern like /privacy/*"
msgstr "Eén per regel: pagina-ID of URL-patroon zoals /privacy/*"

#: admin/views/settings.php:28
msgid "Enter page IDs or URL patterns, one per line."
msgstr "Voer pagina-ID's of URL-patronen in, één per regel."

#: admin/views/settings.php:34
msgid "Hide banner from search engine bots"
msgstr "Verberg banner voor zoekmachinebots"

#: admin/views/settings.php:36
msgid ""
"Automatically detects search engine crawlers (Googlebot, Bingbot, etc.) and "
"skips the banner for them. Improves SEO by serving cleaner HTML to crawlers."
msgstr ""
"Detecteert automatisch zoekmachinecrawlers (Googlebot, Bingbot, enz.) en "
"slaat de banner voor hen over. Verbetert SEO door schoonere HTML te leveren "
"aan crawlers."

#: admin/views/settings.php:42
msgid "Push consent events to GTM Data Layer"
msgstr "Verstuur toestemminggebeurtenissen naar GTM Data Layer"

#: admin/views/settings.php:44
msgid ""
"Pushes a faz_consent_update event with per-category granted/denied values to"
" window.dataLayer after each consent action. Enable if you use Google Tag "
"Manager."
msgstr ""
"Pusht een faz_consent_update event met per-categorie toegestane/geweigerde "
"waarden naar window.dataLayer na elke toestemmingsactie. Activeer dit als je"
" Google Tag Manager gebruikt."

#: admin/views/settings.php:50
msgid "Ad-blocker compatibility mode"
msgstr "Ad-blocker compatibiliteitsmodus"

#: admin/views/settings.php:52
msgid ""
"Uses generic script handle names to prevent ad blockers from blocking the "
"cookie banner. Enable if visitors report the banner not appearing."
msgstr ""
"Gebruikt generieke scripthandlenamen om adblockers te voorkomen dat ze de "
"cookie-banner blokkeren. Activeer dit als bezoekers melden dat de banner "
"niet verschijnt."

#: admin/views/settings.php:58
msgid "Enable per-service consent"
msgstr "Per-dienst toestemming activeren"

#: admin/views/settings.php:60
msgid ""
"When enabled, visitors can accept or reject individual services (e.g., "
"Google Analytics, YouTube) instead of entire categories. This provides more "
"granular privacy control but makes the preference center more complex."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer ingeschakeld, kunnen bezoekers individuele diensten accepteren of "
"weigeren (bijv. Google Analytics, YouTube) in plaats van volledige "
"categorieën. Dit biedt meer gedetailleerde privacycontrole, maar maakt het "
"voorkeurscentrum complexer."

#: admin/views/settings.php:66
msgid "Share consent across subdomains"
msgstr "Toestemming delen via subdomeinen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:68
msgid ""
"Scope the consent cookie to your registrable domain (e.g. .example.com) so "
"it is shared across www, shop, app, etc. Recommended only when all "
"subdomains belong to you and are covered by the same privacy policy. Public-"
"suffix-aware for multi-level TLDs (.co.uk, .com.au)."
msgstr ""
"Beperk de toestemmingscookie tot uw registreerbaar domein (bijv. "
".example.com) zodat deze gedeeld wordt via www, shop, app, enz. Alleen "
"aanbevolen wanneer alle subdomeinen van u zijn en gedekt worden door "
"hetzelfde privacybeleid. Ondersteunt public-suffix voor multi-level TLD’s "
"(.co.uk, .com.au)."

#: admin/views/settings.php:75 admin/views/system-status.php:87
msgid "Cross-Domain Consent"
msgstr "Cross-Domain Consent"

#: admin/views/settings.php:82
msgid "Enable cross-domain consent forwarding"
msgstr "Schakel cross-domain toestemmingsdoorsturing in"

#: admin/views/settings.php:84
msgid ""
"Share consent choices across multiple domains. When a visitor accepts or "
"rejects cookies on one domain, the same choice is forwarded to all "
"configured target domains via secure postMessage."
msgstr ""
"Deel toestemmingskeuzes over meerdere domeinen. Wanneer een bezoeker cookies"
" accepteert of weigert op één domein, wordt dezelfde keuze via beveiligde "
"postMessage doorgestuurd naar alle geconfigureerde doeldomeinen."

#: admin/views/settings.php:87
msgid "Target Domains"
msgstr "Doel domeinen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:88
msgid "One per line: https://shop.example.com"
msgstr "Een per regel: https://shop.example.com"

#: admin/views/settings.php:89
msgid ""
"Full URLs of other sites that should receive consent state. Each site must "
"also have FAZ Cookie Manager installed. One URL per line."
msgstr ""
"Volledige URL's van andere sites die toestand van toestemming moeten "
"ontvangen. Elke site moet ook FAZ Cookie Manager geïnstalleerd hebben. Een "
"URL per regel."

#: admin/views/settings.php:96 admin/views/system-status.php:80
msgid "Pageview Tracking"
msgstr "Paginaweergave tracking"

#: admin/views/settings.php:103
msgid "Enable pageview and banner interaction tracking"
msgstr "Paginaweergave- en bannerinteractietracering inschakelen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:105
msgid ""
"Tracks pageviews and banner interactions (accept, reject, settings) for the "
"dashboard analytics. Data is aggregate-only: it sends the page URL and title"
" with no per-visitor identifier or cookie, so the events cannot be linked "
"across pages or sessions. Counts are stored first-party in your own "
"database. Disable for stricter compliance."
msgstr ""
"Houdt paginaweergaven en bannerinteracties (accepteren, weigeren, "
"instellingen) bij voor de dashboardanalyse. De gegevens zijn uitsluitend "
"geaggregeerd: alleen de pagina-URL en titel worden verzonden, zonder "
"bezoekersidentificatie of cookie, zodat de gebeurtenissen niet over pagina's"
" of sessies heen kunnen worden gekoppeld. De tellingen worden als first "
"party in je eigen database opgeslagen. Schakel uit voor strengere naleving."

#: admin/views/settings.php:112
msgid "Script Blocking"
msgstr "Scriptblokkering"

#: admin/views/settings.php:116
msgid "Pages Excluded from Script Blocking"
msgstr "Pagina's uitgesloten van scriptblokkering"

#: admin/views/settings.php:117
msgid "One per line: /checkout/* or /cart/*"
msgstr "Eén per regel: /checkout/* of /cart/*"

#: admin/views/settings.php:118
msgid ""
"URL patterns where script blocking is disabled (banner still shows). One per"
" line, supports wildcards (e.g. <code>/checkout/*</code>)."
msgstr ""
"URL-patronen waar het blokkeren van scripts is uitgeschakeld (banner wordt "
"nog steeds getoond). Eén per regel, ondersteunt jokers (bijv. "
"<code>/checkout/*</code>)."

#: admin/views/settings.php:121
msgid "Script Blocking Exceptions"
msgstr "Uitzonderingen voor script blokkeren"

#: admin/views/settings.php:122
msgid ""
"One per line: googleapis.com/youtube/v3, recaptcha, my-inline-script-id"
msgstr ""
"Één per regel: googleapis.com/youtube/v3, recaptcha, my-inline-script-id"

#: admin/views/settings.php:123
msgid ""
"Scripts that should never be blocked, even before consent. One per line. "
"Accepts three types of pattern:<br>- <strong>URL fragment</strong> (contains"
" <code>.</code> or <code>/</code>): matched against the script's "
"<code>src</code> or related URL attribute, e.g. "
"<code>googleapis.com/youtube/v3</code>.<br>- <strong>Script ID</strong> (no "
"dots/slashes): matched against the <code>id</code> attribute of the script "
"tag, e.g. <code>my-product-form-data</code>.<br>- <strong>CSS class</strong>"
" (no dots/slashes): matched against the script's <code>class</code> "
"attribute, e.g. <code>recaptcha</code>.<br>These exceptions bypass blocking "
"entirely. Use them only for scripts that genuinely do not set tracking "
"cookies. <strong>Be specific</strong> to avoid accidentally unblocking "
"trackers.<br><strong>Tip:</strong> You can also add <code>class=\"faz-"
"skip\"</code> directly to any script tag to exclude it without adding "
"anything here — no configuration needed."
msgstr ""
"Scripts die nooit geblokkeerd mogen worden, zelfs niet vóór toestemming. Één"
" per regel. Accepteert drie typen patronen:<br>- <strong>URL-"
"fragment</strong> (bevat <code>.</code> of <code>/</code>): vergeleken met "
"het <code>src</code>-attribuut van het script of een gerelateerde URL, bijv."
" <code>googleapis.com/youtube/v3</code>.<br>- <strong>Script-ID</strong> "
"(geen punten/slashes): vergeleken met het <code>id</code>-attribuut van de "
"script-tag, bijv. <code>my-product-form-data</code>.<br>- <strong>CSS-"
"klasse</strong> (geen punten/slashes): vergeleken met het "
"<code>class</code>-attribuut van het script, bijv. "
"<code>recaptcha</code>.<br>Deze uitzonderingen omzeilen blokkering volledig."
" Gebruik ze alleen voor scripts die werkelijk geen trackingcookies plaatsen."
" <strong>Wees specifiek</strong> om per ongeluk trackers te "
"deblokkeren.<br><strong>Tip:</strong> u kunt ook <code>class=\"faz-"
"skip\"</code> rechtstreeks aan een script-tag toevoegen om het uit te "
"sluiten zonder hier iets toe te voegen — geen configuratie nodig."

#: admin/views/settings.php:137
msgid "Enable consent logging"
msgstr "Logboek voor toestemming inschakelen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:139
msgid ""
"Records each visitor's consent choice (accepted, rejected, or partial) for "
"GDPR accountability. Required by Art. 7(1) GDPR to demonstrate that consent "
"was given."
msgstr ""
"Registreert de keuze van elke bezoeker (geaccepteerd, geweigerd of "
"gedeeltelijk) voor GDPR-verantwoording. Vereist volgens artikel 7(1) GDPR om"
" aan te tonen dat toestemming is gegeven."

#: admin/views/settings.php:142
msgid "Retention Period (months)"
msgstr "Bewaartermijn (maanden)"

#: admin/views/settings.php:144
msgid ""
"How long consent records are kept before automatic deletion. Most DPAs "
"recommend 12 months. Logs older than this period are purged daily."
msgstr ""
"Hoe lang toestemmingsrecords worden bewaard voordat ze automatisch worden "
"verwijderd. De meeste DPAs raden 12 maanden aan. Logboeken ouder dan deze "
"periode worden dagelijks verwijderd."

#: admin/views/settings.php:151
msgid "Scanner"
msgstr "Scanner"

#: admin/views/settings.php:155
msgid "Max Pages to Scan"
msgstr "Maximum aantal pagina's om te scannen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:157
msgid ""
"Maximum number of pages the cookie scanner will crawl. Higher values find "
"more cookies but take longer. 100 pages is sufficient for most sites."
msgstr ""
"Het maximum aantal pagina's dat de cookie scanner doorzoekt. Hogere waarden "
"vinden meer cookies maar nemen langer in beslag. 100 pagina's is voldoende "
"voor de meeste sites."

#: admin/views/settings.php:163
msgid "Scanner Debug Mode"
msgstr "Foutopsporingsmodus scanner"

#: admin/views/settings.php:165
msgid ""
"When enabled, the scanner logs every categorization decision. Download logs "
"from the Cookies page."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer ingeschakeld, registreert de scanner elke categorisatiebeslissing. "
"Download logs van de Cookies-pagina."

#: admin/views/settings.php:172
msgid "Automatic Scanning"
msgstr "Automatisch scannen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:179
msgid "Enable automatic cookie scanning"
msgstr "Activeer automatisch cookie-scannen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:181
msgid ""
"Automatically scan your site for new cookies on a schedule. You will receive"
" an email notification if new uncategorized cookies are found."
msgstr ""
"Je site wordt automatisch op nieuwe cookies gescand volgens een schema. Je "
"ontvangt een e-mailmelding als er nieuwe niet-gecategoriseerde cookies "
"worden gevonden."

#: admin/views/settings.php:184
msgid "Scan Frequency"
msgstr "Scan Frequentie"

#: admin/views/settings.php:186
msgid "Daily"
msgstr "Dagelijks"

#: admin/views/settings.php:187 includes/class-activator.php:199
msgid "Weekly"
msgstr "Wekelijks"

#: admin/views/settings.php:188
msgid "Monthly"
msgstr "Maandelijks"

#: admin/views/settings.php:190
msgid ""
"How often the scanner runs automatically. Weekly is recommended for most "
"sites."
msgstr ""
"Hoe vaak de scanner automatisch wordt uitgevoerd. Wekelijks wordt aanbevolen"
" voor de meeste sites."

#: admin/views/settings.php:197
msgid "Microsoft Consent APIs"
msgstr "Microsoft Consent API's"

#: admin/views/settings.php:204
msgid "Microsoft UET Consent Mode"
msgstr "Microsoft UET Consent Modus"

#: admin/views/settings.php:206
msgid ""
"Signals consent status to Microsoft Advertising (Bing Ads) via the UET tag. "
"Enable if you use Microsoft Advertising and need to respect consent for ad "
"tracking."
msgstr ""
"Geeft de toestemmingsstatus door aan Microsoft Advertising (Bing Ads) via de"
" UET-tag. Schakel dit in als je Microsoft Advertising gebruikt en "
"toestemming voor advertentietracering moet respecteren."

#: admin/views/settings.php:212
msgid "Microsoft Clarity Consent API"
msgstr "Microsoft Clarity toestemmings-API"

#: admin/views/settings.php:214
msgid ""
"Signals consent status to Microsoft Clarity (heatmaps and session "
"recordings). Enable if you use Clarity and want it to pause tracking until "
"consent is given."
msgstr ""
"Geeft de toestemmingsstatus door aan Microsoft Clarity (heatmap en "
"sessieopnamen). Schakel dit in als je Clarity gebruikt en wilt dat het de "
"tracking pauzeert tot toestemming is gegeven."

#: admin/views/settings.php:221
msgid "Age Verification"
msgstr "Leeftijdsverificatie"

#: admin/views/settings.php:228
msgid "Require age verification for consent"
msgstr "Vereist leeftijdsverificatie voor toestemming"

#: admin/views/settings.php:230
msgid ""
"Under GDPR Art. 8, children below the minimum age cannot give valid consent "
"for data processing. When enabled, visitors must confirm they meet the "
"minimum age before accepting optional cookies."
msgstr ""
"Volgens GDPR Art. 8 kunnen kinderen onder de minimumleeftijd geen geldige "
"toestemming geven voor gegevensverwerking. Indien ingeschakeld, moeten "
"bezoekers bevestigen dat ze de minimumleeftijd hebben bereikt voordat ze "
"optionele cookies accepteren."

#: admin/views/settings.php:233
msgid "Minimum Age"
msgstr "Minimumleeftijd"

#: admin/views/settings.php:235
msgid ""
"GDPR default is 16. Some EU member states allow 13-15. Check your local law."
msgstr ""
"GDPR-standaard is 16. Sommige EU-lidstaten staan 13-15 toe. Controleer je "
"lokale wetgeving."

#: admin/views/settings.php:242
msgid "IAB TCF"
msgstr "IAB TCF"

#: admin/views/settings.php:249
msgid "Enable IAB TCF v2.3"
msgstr "IAB TCF v2.3 inschakelen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:251
msgid ""
"Enables the IAB Transparency & Consent Framework. Required if you work with "
"ad-tech vendors that need a standardised TC String for programmatic "
"advertising in the EU."
msgstr ""
"Het IAB Transparency & Consent Framework inschakelen. Vereist als je werkt "
"met ad-tech leveranciers die een gestandaardiseerde TC String nodig hebben "
"voor programmatische adverteren in de EU."

#: admin/views/settings.php:254
msgid "Publisher Country Code"
msgstr "Landcode uitgever"

#: admin/views/settings.php:256
msgid ""
"ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 code of the publisher's country (e.g. IT, DE, FR). Used "
"in the TCF consent string."
msgstr ""
"ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 code van het land van de uitgever (bijv. IT, DE, FR). "
"Wordt gebruikt in de TCF toestemmingsreeks."

#: admin/views/settings.php:259
msgid "CMP ID"
msgstr "CMP ID"

#: admin/views/settings.php:261
msgid ""
"Your registered IAB CMP ID (<a href=\"https://iabeurope.eu/cmp-list/\" "
"target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IAB CMP List</a>). With "
"ID&nbsp;0 the banner and cookie blocking work normally, but ad-tech vendors "
"will ignore the TC String. Google Consent Mode v2 works regardless of CMP "
"registration."
msgstr ""
"Je geregistreerde IAB CMP ID (<a href=\"https://iabeurope.eu/cmp-list/\" "
"target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IAB CMP List</a>). Met "
"ID&nbsp;0 werkt de banner en cookieblokkering normaal, maar ad-tech "
"leveranciers negeren de TC String. Google Consent Mode v2 werkt ongeacht CMP"
" registratie."

#: admin/views/settings.php:267
msgid "Purpose One Treatment"
msgstr "Doel Een Behandeling"

#: admin/views/settings.php:269
msgid ""
"Set to true if Purpose 1 consent was NOT disclosed (e.g. publisher in a "
"country where Purpose 1 is not required)."
msgstr ""
"Ingesteld op waar als toestemming voor Doel 1 NIET is vrijgegeven "
"(bijvoorbeeld uitgever in een land waar Doel 1 niet vereist is)."

#: admin/views/settings.php:273
msgid "Loading GVL status..."
msgstr "GVL-status laden..."

#: admin/views/settings.php:282 admin/views/system-status.php:82
msgid "Geo-Targeting"
msgstr "Geo-doelgroep"

#: admin/views/settings.php:289
msgid "Enable geo-targeted banner display"
msgstr "Geo-doelgroepbanners weergeven inschakelen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:291
msgid ""
"Show the cookie banner only to visitors from specific regions. Requires a "
"MaxMind GeoLite2 database (configured below) or Cloudflare CF-IPCountry "
"header."
msgstr ""
"Toon de cookiewaarschuwing alleen aan bezoekers uit specifieke regioën. "
"Vereist een MaxMind GeoLite2-database (hieronder geconfigureerd) of "
"Cloudflare CF-IPCountry-header."

#: admin/views/settings.php:294
msgid "Target Regions"
msgstr "Doelregioën"

#: admin/views/settings.php:298
msgid "EU / EEA"
msgstr "EU / EER"

#: admin/views/settings.php:299
msgid "United Kingdom"
msgstr "Verenigd Koninkrijk"

#: admin/views/settings.php:300
msgid "United States"
msgstr "Verenigde Staten"

#: admin/views/settings.php:301
msgid "Canada"
msgstr "Canada"

#: admin/views/settings.php:302
msgid "Brazil"
msgstr "Brazilië"

#: admin/views/settings.php:304
msgid "Japan"
msgstr "Japan"

#: admin/views/settings.php:305
msgid "Switzerland"
msgstr "Zwitserland"

#: admin/views/settings.php:315
msgid ""
"Select which regions should see the cookie banner. Visitors from other "
"regions will not see it (if \"Hide banner\" is selected below)."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer welke regioén de cookiewaarschuwing moeten zien. Bezoekers uit "
"andere regioén zien deze niet (als \"Waarschuwing verbergen\" hieronder is "
"geselecteerd)."

#: admin/views/settings.php:318
msgid "Non-target visitors"
msgstr "Bezoekers die niet als doelgroep zijn gekozen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:320
msgid "Show banner anyway (safest)"
msgstr "Toon banner toch (veiligste)"

#: admin/views/settings.php:321
msgid "Hide banner (scripts load normally)"
msgstr "Verberg banner (scripts laden normaal)"

#: admin/views/settings.php:323
msgid ""
"What happens when a visitor is from outside the target regions. \"Show "
"banner anyway\" is the safest option and recommended for sites with global "
"audiences."
msgstr ""
"Wat er gebeurt wanneer een bezoeker vandaan komt buiten de doelgebieden. "
"\"Toon banner toch\" is de veiligste optie en wordt aanbevolen voor sites "
"met wereldwijde publieken."

#: admin/views/settings.php:330
msgid "GeoIP Database (MaxMind GeoLite2)"
msgstr "GeoIP-database (MaxMind GeoLite2)"

#: admin/views/settings.php:334
msgid ""
"Geo-targeting requires a MaxMind GeoLite2 database. <a "
"href=\"https://www.maxmind.com/en/geolite2/signup\" target=\"_blank\" "
"rel=\"noopener\">Get a free license key</a>."
msgstr ""
"Geo-targeting vereist een MaxMind GeoLite2-database. <a "
"href=\"https://www.maxmind.com/en/geolite2/signup\" target=\"_blank\" "
"rel=\"noopener\">Vraag een gratis licentiesleutel aan</a>."

#: admin/views/settings.php:337
msgid "Database edition"
msgstr "Database-editie"

#: admin/views/settings.php:339
msgid "Country &#8212; country-level only (recommended)"
msgstr "Country &#8212; alleen op landniveau (aanbevolen)"

#: admin/views/settings.php:340
msgid "City &#8212; adds region / state detection"
msgstr "City &#8212; voegt detectie van regio/staat toe"

#: admin/views/settings.php:343
msgid ""
"<strong>Country</strong> (~10 MB) resolves the visitor&#8217;s country only "
"&#8212; enough for country-based banner targeting and most per-jurisdiction "
"rules. <strong>City</strong> (~60&#8211;110 MB) additionally resolves the "
"region / province / state, which a few rules need: sub-national regimes such"
" as <em>Quebec Law 25</em> apply only inside one region of a country, so "
"without City (or a Cloudflare <code>CF-Region-Code</code> header) the plugin"
" can only see &#8220;Canada&#8221; and cannot route that visitor to the "
"Quebec ruleset. Choose City only if you rely on region-level routing &#8212;"
" it is a much larger download. Changing this and clicking &#8220;Update "
"Database&#8221; replaces the installed database."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Country</strong> (~10 MB) bepaalt alleen het land van de bezoeker "
"&#8212; voldoende voor landgebaseerde bannertargeting en de meeste regels "
"per rechtsgebied. <strong>City</strong> (~60&#8211;110 MB) bepaalt daarnaast"
" de regio / provincie / staat, wat enkele regels nodig hebben: subnationale "
"regimes zoals de <em>Quebec Wet 25</em> gelden alleen binnen één regio van "
"een land, dus zonder City (of een Cloudflare-header <code>CF-Region-"
"Code</code>) ziet de plug-in alleen &#8220;Canada&#8221; en kan die bezoeker"
" niet naar de Quebec-ruleset routeren. Kies City alleen als u afhankelijk "
"bent van routing op regioniveau &#8212; het is een veel grotere download. "
"Door dit te wijzigen en op &#8220;Database bijwerken&#8221; te klikken, "
"wordt de geïnstalleerde database vervangen."

#: admin/views/settings.php:347
msgid "MaxMind License Key"
msgstr "MaxMind Licentiesleutel"

#: admin/views/settings.php:348
msgid "Enter your MaxMind license key"
msgstr "Voer je MaxMind licentiesleutel in"

#: admin/views/settings.php:352
msgid "Update Database"
msgstr "Database bijwerken"

#: admin/views/settings.php:358
msgid "Data Management"
msgstr "Gegevensbeheer"

#: admin/views/settings.php:365
msgid "Remove all data on uninstall"
msgstr "Alle gegevens verwijderen bij verwijdering"

#: admin/views/settings.php:367
msgid ""
"When enabled, deleting the plugin will permanently remove ALL data: cookies,"
" categories, consent logs, pageviews, banner settings, and scan history. "
"Keep this OFF if you plan to reinstall or update the plugin."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer ingeschakeld, worden bij het verwijderen van de plugin ALLE gegevens"
" definitief verwijderd: cookies, categorieën, toestemmingslogs, "
"paginaweergaven, bannerinstellingen en scangeschiedenis. Houd deze optie UIT"
" als u de plugin opnieuw wilt installeren of bijwerken."

#: admin/views/settings.php:375
msgid "Paid Memberships Pro integration"
msgstr "Paid Memberships Pro-integratie"

#: admin/views/settings.php:379
msgid ""
"Implement a \"Pay-or-Accept\" model: logged-in members on selected PMP "
"levels skip the cookie banner and have consent <strong>programmatically "
"recorded as granted for all categories</strong> via a server-side cookie. "
"Marketing, analytics, functional and other non-necessary scripts will run "
"for them without an explicit banner interaction. Free visitors continue to "
"see the standard banner and consent flow."
msgstr ""
"Implementeer een \"Betalen of Accepteren\"-model: ingelogde leden met "
"geselecteerde PMP-niveaus slaan de cookiebanner over en krijgen toestemming "
"<strong>programmatisch vastgelegd als verleend voor alle "
"categorieën</strong> via een server-side cookie. Marketing-, analyse-, "
"functionele en andere niet-noodzakelijke scripts worden voor hen uitgevoerd "
"zonder expliciete bannerinteractie. Gratis bezoekers blijven de "
"standaardbanner en het toestemmingsproces zien."

#: admin/views/settings.php:382
msgid "Legal note:"
msgstr "Juridische opmerking:"

#: admin/views/settings.php:383
msgid ""
"Because this option grants consent on behalf of the member (it does not "
"merely hide the banner), you must disclose it clearly in your Terms of "
"Service, Privacy Policy, and at the point of subscription so the membership "
"fee is understood as a genuine alternative to giving consent (EDPB Opinion "
"08/2024). Members must remain able to revoke or adjust their consent at any "
"time via the standard revisit widget."
msgstr ""
"Omdat deze optie toestemming verleent namens het lid (en niet alleen de "
"banner verbergt), moet u dit duidelijk vermelden in uw Servicevoorwaarden, "
"Privacybeleid en bij het moment van inschrijving, zodat het "
"lidmaatschapsgeld wordt begrepen als een oprecht alternatief voor het geven "
"van toestemming (EDPB-advies 08/2024). Leden moeten op elk moment "
"toestemming kunnen intrekken of aanpassen via de standaard revisit-widget."

#: admin/views/settings.php:389
msgid "Enable PMP integration"
msgstr "PMP-integratie inschakelen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:393
msgid "Exempt membership level IDs"
msgstr "Vrijgestelde lidmaatschapsniveau-ID's"

#: admin/views/settings.php:394
msgid "e.g. 2, 3, 5"
msgstr "bijv. 2, 3, 5"

#: admin/views/settings.php:396
msgid ""
"Comma-separated PMP level IDs whose members should be exempted. Find level "
"IDs in <strong>Memberships → Settings → Levels</strong>. Leave empty to "
"disable exemption."
msgstr ""
"Kommagescheiden PMP-niveau-ID's waarvan de leden vrijgesteld moeten worden. "
"Vind niveau-ID's in <strong>Memberships → Settings → Levels</strong>. Laat "
"leeg om vrijstelling uit te schakelen."

#: admin/views/settings.php:405
msgid "Force re-consent"
msgstr "Nieuwe toestemming afdwingen"

#: admin/views/settings.php:409
msgid ""
"Show the cookie banner again to all returning visitors. Useful when you "
"change which cookies or services are used on your site (e.g. new AdSense "
"tags, added analytics) and want prior visitors to renew their consent before"
" those services run."
msgstr ""
"Toon de cookiebanner opnieuw aan alle terugkerende bezoekers. Handig wanneer"
" u wijzigt welke cookies of services op uw site worden gebruikt (bijv. "
"nieuwe AdSense-tags, toegevoegde analyses) en wilt dat eerdere bezoekers hun"
" toestemming vernieuwen voordat die services worden uitgevoerd."

#: admin/views/settings.php:412
msgid "Current consent revision"
msgstr "Huidige toestemmingsrevisie"

#: admin/views/settings.php:416
msgid "Invalidate all consents"
msgstr "Alle toestemmingen ongeldig maken"

#: admin/views/settings.php:419
msgid ""
"Visitors whose stored consent has a lower revision will see the banner again"
" on their next visit. This does not affect the current page load."
msgstr ""
"Bezoekers wiens opgeslagen toestemming een lagere revisie heeft, zien de "
"banner opnieuw bij hun volgende bezoek. Dit heeft geen invloed op het laden "
"van de huidige pagina."

